{
  "stem": "6878.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I went to him, and he says, it'll cost you 1 and 1/2 kilograms of bread for me to come to take the child.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I said, quite all right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Come.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I brought him to our place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we warmed up water.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he took out the child, and he was perfect.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the child grew up until he was 18 months.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A little boy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And what was his name?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Henech.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was after my father's name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father was Henech.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we gave him a name after my father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I didn't let him have the bris milah in ghetto, because I said to Ida, if we'll survive, we'll make him a bris, but not now.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Leave it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he had no bris.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What was the reason for that?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Why didn't you want to--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The reason for that was, I had in my mind I'm going to take him out from the ghetto to give it to Lithuanian people to help through the time.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I eventually find a farmer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Shall I come to that a little bit later?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that was when the baby was born in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'll come to that later a little bit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But then we had to register ourselves to work on the airport.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So being an electrician, we were 22 Jewish electricians.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we did all the electrical installations for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They build barracks.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then they built a new airport.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we did the electrical installation in the new airport, all the Yiddish boys.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my foreman on the airport was a Christian guy, which I was quite friendly with him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he used to say to me, take off your star.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we're going to have lunch at the German unit, at the German unit with the Germans army.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
